 	 * Cyrix 486-class CPU does not support rdmsr instruction.
 	 * The rdmsr instruction generates invalid opcode fault, and exception
 	 * will be trapped by bluetrap6() on Cyrix 486-class CPU.  The
@@ -735,10 +740,22 @@
 			}
